    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm a solo developer from Germany, and this is my first game.<br>Thanks to the support of <i>Bagpack Games</i>, I was able to create this first demo, which I plan to expand into a full game later on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We hope you enjoy it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Sanatorium</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/3f5fa3b52df6d4705fe1f905bee6b72d.poster.avif?t=1770023333\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/3f5fa3b52df6d4705fe1f905bee6b72d.webm?t=1770023333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/3f5fa3b52df6d4705fe1f905bee6b72d.mp4?t=1770023333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the environment of the Sanatorium and try to stay calm despite the Horrors that might be hidden in the shadows around every corner.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/c8ccbbea0035ab82e5e78e1fe2377fb9.poster.avif?t=1770023333\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/c8ccbbea0035ab82e5e78e1fe2377fb9.webm?t=1770023333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/c8ccbbea0035ab82e5e78e1fe2377fb9.mp4?t=1770023333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your way through the rooms of the Sanatorium, equipped with nothing but the clothes you wear. Pay close attention to your surroundings and you might find some tools that can help you on your journey. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/c3656be9e22085c3f2f7ebc7ab33b733.poster.avif?t=1770023333\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/c3656be9e22085c3f2f7ebc7ab33b733.webm?t=1770023333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285430/extras/c3656be9e22085c3f2f7ebc7ab33b733.mp4?t=1770023333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes the path might not be clear from the start. Pay close attention to your environment and solve thrilling puzzles to delve deeper into the darkest corners of the Sanatorium.</p>",
